description: This file defines Express.js routes for internal seeding endpoints, used for loading mock data into the database with various seed operations. It includes Swagger API documentation annotations.

methods.name: router.post('/:entity')
methods.description: Endpoint to seed mock data for a specific entity, protected by internalSeedGuard and delegated to seedController.seedOne.

methods.name: router.post('/')
methods.description: Endpoint to seed all entities from .projdefn or provided arrays, protected by internalSeedGuard and delegated to seedController.seedAll.

methods.name: router.post('/all')
methods.description: Endpoint to seed all entities in order, with optional request body, protected by internalSeedGuard and delegated to seedController.seedAll.

methods.name: router.get('/verify')
methods.description: Endpoint to verify the seeded counts for entities, protected by internalSeedGuard and delegated to seedController.verify.
